BE AWARE that a mistake happened so the files of the 32 bits and the 64 bits versions were inverted.

Consequently:
* this 32 bits torrent contains the 64 bits version.
* the 64 bits torrent contains the 32 bits version.
@100bugs - You are right mate. I have corrected the mistake in other sites but i can not edit in tpb. Thanks.
